WEBVTT

00:01.730 --> 00:04.150
<b>Is this the bandits' fortress?</b>

00:04.150 --> 00:05.020
<b>That's right.</b>

00:05.020 --> 00:09.530
<b>Our first major operation as the Jaegers is to bring this place down.</b>

00:09.530 --> 00:10.940
<b>What's our strategy?</b>

00:10.940 --> 00:12.900
<b>Justice is bold.</b>

00:12.900 --> 00:14.740
<b>We attack head-on!</b>

00:20.410 --> 00:23.210
<b>Um, why am I here too?</b>

00:23.210 --> 00:25.750
<b>You're a backup member of the Jaegers.</b>

00:25.750 --> 00:28.880
<b>Observing their operation will be good for you.</b>

00:30.300 --> 00:31.800
<b><i>She's the one who killed Sheele!</i></b>

00:32.970 --> 00:35.220
<b><i>I have to control myself.</i></b>

00:35.220 --> 00:37.050
<b><i>Remember what Bro said.</i></b>

00:37.050 --> 00:39.760
<b><i>Simply being hot-headed won't help.</i></b>

00:39.760 --> 00:43.310
<b><i>I have to get out of here and 
relay this information to the others.</i></b>

00:45.900 --> 00:47.400
<b><i>Wait a second...</i></b>

00:47.400 --> 00:49.770
<b><i>Isn't this the perfect chance to escape?</i></b>

00:54.400 --> 00:56.360
<b><i>So much for that!</i></b>

00:58.120 --> 01:00.830
<b>You've got some nerve, strolling up to the front gates!</b>

01:00.830 --> 01:02.290
<b>Coro, number five.</b>

01:07.710 --> 01:09.250
<b>Kill them!</b>

01:09.960 --> 01:11.550
<b>Judgment of the Ten Kings:</b>

01:12.260 --> 01:14.510
<b>Enma's Spear of Justice!</b>

01:14.510 --> 01:15.380
<b>Next!</b>

01:15.380 --> 01:15.970
<b>Number seven!</b>

01:18.180 --> 01:20.850
<b>Taizan's Cannon of Justice!</b>

01:23.930 --> 01:26.100
<b>How do you like the weapons I created?</b>

01:26.730 --> 01:28.520
<b>The Hands of God, Perfector...</b>

01:28.520 --> 01:31.860
<b>They increase my speed and precision several hundred times over.</b>

01:31.860 --> 01:34.860
<b>Truly the most stylish of all Imperial Relics!</b>

01:40.330 --> 01:44.200
<b>After we're done, I'll put you back together and have some fun,</b>

01:44.200 --> 01:46.290
<b>my little dolls.</b>

01:52.090 --> 01:54.710
<b>Hey, no need to thank me.</b>

01:54.710 --> 01:55.550
<b>We're a team, right?</b>

01:55.550 --> 01:57.380
<b>I knew he was there.</b>

01:57.380 --> 01:58.590
<b>Seriously?</b>

02:00.350 --> 02:02.560
<b>My Imperial Relic is a flamethrower.</b>

02:03.310 --> 02:05.020
<b>The Purgatorial Invitation, Rubicante.</b>

02:05.600 --> 02:07.190
<b>This is just part of the job.</b>

02:09.770 --> 02:10.480
<b>What?</b>

02:13.110 --> 02:15.110
<b>An... angel?</b>

02:16.070 --> 02:17.950
<b>My winged Relic,</b>

02:17.950 --> 02:19.700
<b>the Thousand-Mile Flight, Mastema.</b>

02:20.410 --> 02:22.580
<b>I won't let any of you escape.</b>

