<b><i>But you're stronger than that.</i></b>

20:03.180 --> 20:05.720
<b><i>You have the will to survive.</i></b>

20:09.100 --> 20:10.730
<b><i>It's quite strange.</i></b>

20:11.230 --> 20:14.730
<b><i>I'm sure we'll meet again, Tatsumi.</i></b>

20:15.230 --> 20:17.570
<b><i>No, I'll make sure we do.</i></b>

20:18.150 --> 20:21.240
<b><i>And when that time comes, 
you'll answer to my feelings.</i></b>

20:21.240 --> 20:23.160
<b><i>Prepare yourself, Tatsumi.</i></b>

20:26.120 --> 20:29.870
<b>And that's what I saw of the Jaegers' strength.</b>

